<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v14" title="Q8_v14" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p>
    <p>En una heladería se preparan helados de palito sabor frutilla. En la tarjeta de receta se indica lo siguiente:<br />Para cada helado se usan:<br />- Mezcla base: 4 onzas<br />- Jarabe de frutilla: <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> onzas.</p>
    <p>Se prepararán 180 helados de este sabor. Si se considera que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, ¿cuántos mL de jarabe de frutilla se necesitan en total para los 180 helados?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Según el registro, ¿qué cantidad mantiene correctamente la razón indicada?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">75 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 75 mL corresponden a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>75</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe, que alcanza solo para 1 helado, porque cada helado usa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Para 180 helados se necesitan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">13500 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Cada helado usa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe. Para 180 helados: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Luego, como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13&#160;500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">2160 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 2160 mL corresponden a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2160</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe. Pero para 180 helados se requieren <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, 2160 mL no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">21600 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 21600 mL corresponden a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>21600</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe. Sin embargo, la receta exige <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas para 180 helados. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>720</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta cantidad es mayor que la necesaria.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la cantidad de jarabe por helado</strong></p>
            <p>Cada helado usa <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> onzas de jarabe de frutilla.</p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, cada helado necesita <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mtext> onzas</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular las onzas totales para 180 helados</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, se necesitan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mtext> onzas</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> de jarabe.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir de onzas a mL</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado indica que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mtext> onzas</m:mtext><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13&#160;500</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad total de jarabe de frutilla necesaria para 180 helados es <strong>13 500 mL</strong>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>